{"tid":2229227,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"英媒：英國將推新法案　循非法路線入境者將不獲庇護","createTime":"2020-10-04T08:31:50.000Z","updateTime":"2020-10-04T08:54:06.000Z","uid":339805,"like":4,"dislike":5,"uniUserReply":11,"replies":[{"pid":"17138bf65b52c03a2daefe5868646e0fcff3dbeb","tid":2229227,"uid":339805,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-04T08:31:50.000Z","msg":"《星期日泰晤士報》指，英國政府將會公布一項新的《公平邊界法案》，所有循非法途徑入境的人士，都不會獲庇護。<br />\n<br />\n《星期日泰晤士報》引述英國內政大臣彭黛玲表示，政府將會提出一項《公平邊界法案》（fair borders bill），拒絕向循非法路線入境，或經英倫海峽坐船偷渡入境的人士提供庇護。新法案將同時列明，將開放新設施來收容和處理尋求庇護者，沒有面臨危險的外國罪犯及尋求庇護者將被驅逐出境。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.thestandnews.com/international/%E8%8B%B1%E5%AA%92-%E8%8B%B1%E5%9C%8B%E5%B0%87%E6%8E%A8%E6%96%B0%E6%B3%95%E6%A1%88-%E5%BE%AA%E9%9D%9E%E6%B3%95%E8%B7%AF%E7%B7%9A%E5%85%A5%E5%A2%83%E8%80%85%E5%B0%87%E4%B8%8D%E7%8D%B2%E5%BA%87%E8%AD%B7/?fbclid=IwAR0ptQvFLybOVb6yeCXSyHAfebBFk6YYmOqvL_KU1p8U2szbGBHnAbq1qII\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thestandnews.com%2Finternational%2F%25E8%258B%25B1%25E5%25AA%2592-%25E8%258B%25B1%25E5%259C%258B%25E5%25B0%2587%25E6%258E%25A8%25E6%2596%25B0%25E6%25B3%2595%25E6%25A1%2588-%25E5%25BE%25AA%25E9%259D%259E%25E6%25B3%2595%25E8%25B7%25AF%25E7%25B7%259A%25E5%2585%25A5%25E5%25A2%2583%25E8%2580%2585%25E5%25B0%2587%25E4%25B8%258D%25E7%258D%25B2%25E5%25BA%2587%25E8%25AD%25B7%2F%3Ffbclid%3DIwAR0ptQvFLybOVb6yeCXSyHAfebBFk6YYmOqvL_KU1p8U2szbGBHnAbq1qII&d=eUEb8trTAlhqW9E3j8wil%2ByReoVNKXL6ewaNyEagWdY%3D&h=155de6f5\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thestandnews.com%2Finternational%2F%25E8%258B%25B1%25E5%25AA%2592-%25E8%258B%25B1%25E5%259C%258B%25E5%25B0%2587%25E6%258E%25A8%25E6%2596%25B0%25E6%25B3%2595%25E6%25A1%2588-%25E5%25BE%25AA%25E9%259D%259E%25E6%25B3%2595%25E8%25B7%25AF%25E7%25B7%259A%25E5%2585%25A5%25E5%25A2%2583%25E8%2580%2585%25E5%25B0%2587%25E4%25B8%258D%25E7%258D%25B2%25E5%25BA%2587%25E8%25AD%25B7%2F%3Ffbclid%3DIwAR0ptQvFLybOVb6yeCXSyHAfebBFk6YYmOqvL_KU1p8U2szbGBHnAbq1qI